            <p>Born in 1968 <br />Domicile: Oslo </p>
<p><strong>Education</strong><br clear="all" />1988- University Preliminary Entrance Examination (Ex. phil.) from the University of Oslo <br clear="all" />1993- Intermediate Subject in Economics, University of Tromsø<br clear="all" />1996-2000- Graduate Studies in Economics, University of Oslo </p>
<p align="left"><strong>Work Experience<br /></strong>Roger Schjerva has work experience from various areas, including organisational work, construction, the hotel business, and nursing and social work. </p>
<p align="left"><strong>Other</strong><br />1998- Mr Schjerva has worked for the Socialist Left Party's Parliament Group as Financial Adviser and Leader of Secretariat. <br />He has also held various political positions, including Political Secretary, County Councillor, and Member of the Board of Oslo Socialist Left Party. <br /><br /></p>
